Architecture of Medical QA System

User Query
     |
     ↓
Sentence Transformer Model
     |
     ↓
Query Embedding
     |
     ↓
FAISS Vector Search
     |
     ↓
Similarity Matching
     |
     ↓
Relevant Medical Answers


Components:

1. Dataset Layer
   - MedQuAD CSV dataset

2. Embedding Layer
   - Sentence Transformer converts text into vectors

3. Search Layer
   - FAISS performs similarity search

4. Output Layer
   - Displays retrieved answers